entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully rescued the sixth Imperial Officer from the Rebel Detainment Facility.
entries.journal_entry_description: Search the Rebel Detainment Facility for the next Imperial Officer being held there
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeat SpecForce Veterans in the Hospital located in the Eastern-most room of the Detention Facility.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat Chard Fristena in combat and take his Jedi Robe.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Get the disguise from Chard Fristena
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Search the holding cells located at the Southeast holding wing of the facility.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Give the officer the disguise you have.
